      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:27]</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r {2d6}[poison]]]{2d6 poison damage} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r {2d6}[poison]]]{2d6 poison damage}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2}, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r {2d6}[poison]]]{2d6 poison damage}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2}, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 2} (1 round)</p>"
